  <h2>About Kale</h2>

  <p class="tagline">
    Cold-hardy greens with one of the longest harvest windows in short seasons.
  </p>

  <p class="lede">
    <strong>Kale is one of the most frost-tolerant vegetables you can grow.</strong>
    It keeps producing in cool weather that slows most crops, and light freezes typically improve flavor rather than causing damage.
  </p>

  <p>
    Use the <a href="/tools/seed-start-planner/">Seed Starting Planner</a>
